show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Vikas, once mocked as a broke “loser boyfriend,” secretly lives a double life — as the mysterious Secret Rockstar and the viral sensation Guitar King. When his gold-digging ex Aastha teams up with a rival to publicly humiliate him, Vikas shocks everyone by revealing his true identity on a grand stage. The rags-to-riches twist turns heartbreak into triumph, winning back his true love Meenal while leaving his enemies stunned and disgraced
